    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2019 sedan in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents, with some paint wear in areas. The interior shows noticeable use \u2014 upholstery has wear marks and there are scuffs on trim surfaces. Mechanically functional but shows its age and use. Priced accordingly.",
      "price": 20000.0,
